claim.t.sol
├── when the campaign has expired
│  └── it should revert
└── when the campaign has not expired
   ├── when the recipient has already claimed
   │  └── it should revert
   └── when the recipient has not claimed
      ├── when the claim is not included in the merkle tree
      │  ├── when the index is not valid
      │  │  └── it should revert
      │  ├── when the recipient address is not valid
      │  │  └── it should revert
      │  └── when the merkle proof is not valid
      │     └── it should revert
      └── when the claim is included in the merkle tree
         ├── it should mark the index as claimed
         ├── it should create a lockup linear airstream
         └── it should emit a {Claim} event
